sec.p:
Semi-structured interviews will be held with the following:
people who declined the postal invitation to take part in the trial (‘decliners’), but were willing to be interviewed about their reasons for declining (n = 15);
participants who have completed their (6-month) primary outcome measures for the trial (n = 30);
participants who have completed their (12-month) outcome measures for the trial (‘exit interviews’, n = 30);
trial CBT therapists (n = 9) and their clinical supervisors (n = 3).
